oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Acuff Rose acetates - part 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various recordings of performances by George Morgan [unconfirmed], Fred Rose (performer), Jimmie Davis (performer), Hank Williams (performer), Beasley Smith (Performer), Jimmie Dickens (performer), Audrey Williams (performer), and Molly O'Day (performer).
